    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have got to see this absolute beauty! It is in truly stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, keeping it tucked away in the garage and sparkling clean. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh car smell! I'm looking for a quick sale, so I've priced it to move. First person to see it is going to fall in love! \u2728",
      "price": 43500.0,
