    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a superlative 2001 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This S54B32 powerhouse maintains factory-perfect tolerances, featuring a high-pressure double-VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous atmospheric induction. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. Every bushing has been refreshed with OEM rubber to preserve the legendary handling dynamics. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior bolsters show no signs of compression or wear. Maintenance is current, including a recent valve adjustment and rod bearing preventative service. This is a rare, turn-key investment for an enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
